http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/kozhikode/Posting-on-daily-wages-for-nursing-assistants/article14010041.ece

: Nursing assistants are being posted on daily wage basis at hospitals associated with the Government Medical College in Kozhikode. Those who have retired as nursing assistants from the Department of Health or the Department of Medical Education and those who have not crossed 60 years of age can apply. Interested candidates should report at the Principal’s office at 11 a.m. on January 22. They have to produce documents to prove their date of birth and experience. The posting will be for either 179 days or till permanent employees are posted, a press release said.— Staff Reporter